{
    "title": "Natural Mystic",
    "artist": "Bob Marley",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro]\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">There's a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If you listen carefully now you will hear</span>\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">This could be the first trumpet</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Might as well be the last</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Many more will have to suffer</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Many more will have to die</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Don't ask me why</span>\n\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Things are not the way, they used to be</span>\n               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I won't tell, no lie</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">One and all got to face, reality now</span>\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Though I try to find the answer</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">To all the questions they ask</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Though I know it's impossible</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">To go living through the past</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Don't tell no lie</span>\n\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">There's a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Can't keep them down</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If you listen carefully now you will hear</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Such a natural mystic</span>\n           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n\n            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">This could be the first trumpet</span>\n          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Might as well be the last</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Many more will have to suffer</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Many more will have to die</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Don't ask me why</span>\n\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">There's a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">I won't tell no lie</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">If you listen carefully now, you will hear</span>\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">There's a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Such a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n\n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Dm\">Dm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Such a natural mystic</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Blowing through the air</span>\n",
